        "summary": "A complete onboarding experience now greets new users with a welcome modal, a progress checklist, and automatic task tracking wired into the desktop shell.",
        "items": [
          {
            "text": "New users are now welcomed by a 2-step intro modal showing the AURA logo and a preview of getting-started tasks on first login, with a skip option and analytics tracking. Onboarding state persists per user via a Zustand store backed by localStorage, so progress survives reloads and is scoped to each account.",
