            "confidence": "high"
          },
          {
            "text": "A floating, collapsible checklist widget anchored to the bottom-right of the desktop guides users through five concrete first tasks — sending a message, creating a project, creating an agent, generating an image with AURA 3D, and exploring plans & credits — with a progress bar and click-through navigation to each feature.",
            "commit_shas": [
              "708e75e6a2f331a85237b0a1add008371b631519",
              "bd804201205eb0d6fa131e14e53f6e7bf1cc6066"
            ],
            "confidence": "high"
          },
          {
            "text": "Checklist items now tick off automatically: a centralized task watcher subscribes to the message, projects, agents, 3D, and billing stores and emits per-task and completion analytics events, so users never have to manually mark progress.",
