              "6f91ff35d4277c128be32eb41b64fb374637c94c"
            ],
            "confidence": "high"
          },
          {
            "text": "A new Help button sits in the BottomTaskbar between Settings and Profile, letting users reopen the checklist after dismissing it or restart onboarding once it's complete. The welcome modal, checklist, and watcher are mounted in AppShell behind lazy boundaries, and a small CSS fix re-centers task icons with their labels in the welcome preview.",
